text:
🌳🚴Punggol West Bank Park Connector runs from Sengkang West Way to Sengkang West Ave.
🌳🌲🍂This scenic Park Connector snakes along the west bank of Sungei Punggol.
🍂Towards the end of the Park Connector is a View Deck where you can enjoy a panoramic view of the water body and it's lush surrounding.
